lead_paragraph: England have named an unchanged squad for their tour of India with their all-time leading wicket-taker James Anderson not included in the initial 16-man list for the five-test series, the England and Wales Cricket Board (ECB) said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Anderson Absent Again as England Unchanged for India Tour
headline.main: Anderson Absent Again as England Unchanged for India Tour
